NAME
        mail <names>

DESCRIPTION
        Communications is one of the building blocks of society. There are post
        office scattered around the realms.

ARGUMENTS
	<names> - One or more people or groups to send a message to. Names can
                  be comma or space separated. A message can be sent to all
                  wizards of a domain, or to groups as set with an alias. The
                  local post office may define groups of people, too.

SEE ALSO
        mail_system, malias, vitals mail
